973
01:04:49,929 --> 01:04:51,681
- Yeah?
- Have I got a fight for you.

974
01:04:51,848 --> 01:04:54,559
Saturday night.
Guaranteed four grand.

975
01:04:54,726 --> 01:04:56,060
Seven if he wins.

976
01:04:56,227 --> 01:04:58,354
