You're on. Let's go!

977
01:05:07,572 --> 01:05:11,618
Bailey, it's me. He won.

978
01:05:11,785 --> 01:05:14,037
Can you believe that?
The kid's robot actually won.

979
01:05:16,164 --> 01:05:17,248
I know.

980
01:05:19,501 --> 01:05:22,045
Oh, yeah, oh, happy?
Oh, my God. Yeah.

981
01:05:22,212 --> 01:05:24,631
He's been bit.
He's been bit real bad.

982
01:05:27,258 --> 01:05:29,427
Yeah. Anyway, I...

983
01:05:31,763 --> 01:05:33,473
...I just wanted you to know.

