1032
01:09:39,510 --> 01:09:42,513
They had their personas.
They all had flair.

1033
01:09:42,680 --> 01:09:44,932
Now you? You might
not have much robot,

1034
01:09:45,099 --> 01:09:47,143
but with that dance,
you got flair.

1035
01:09:47,310 --> 01:09:50,605
Plus, you're a kid.
People love that kid thing.

1036
01:09:50,772 --> 01:09:53,399
- What are you? Like nine? Ten?
- I'm 11.

1037
01:09:53,566 --> 01:09:55,693
OK. Are you sure you're 11?

1038
01:09:55,860 --> 01:09:58,613
Yes. I'm sure I'm 11.

1039
01:10:00,031 --> 01:10:03,034
Anyway, the point
is people want to see that.

1040
01:10:06,621 --> 01:10:08,539
You're really not messing with me?

1041
01:10:08,706 --> 01:10:11,084
I am not messing with you.
They're going to love it.

1042
01:10:14,337 --> 01:10:15,505
- OK.
- Cool.

1043
01:10:15,671 --> 01:10:16,923
- But...
- What?

1044
01:10:17,090 --> 01:10:19,592
I won't do it unless you help me.

1045
01:10:21,594 --> 01:10:23,054
[chuckles] I can't dance.
You're on your own there.

1046
01:10:23,221 --> 01:10:25,223
No. Boxing.

1047
01:10:25,389 --> 01:10:26,724
- Oh, I see.
- I program the robot.

1048
01:10:26,891 --> 01:10:29,060
- You teach him to box.
- And you dance.

1049
01:10:29,227 --> 01:10:30,561
And you dance.

1050
01:10:32,897 --> 01:10:34,107
- Yeah.
- Yeah?

1051
01:10:34,273 --> 01:10:37,193
- Deal.
- [chuckles]

1052
01:10:37,360 --> 01:10:38,444
Deal.

1053
01:10:39,612 --> 01:10:41,489
All right.

1054
01:10:41,656 --> 01:10:42,990
It's going to be cool.

1055
01:11:04,470 --> 01:11:05,596
[sighs]

1056
01:11:37,795 --> 01:11:38,880
Nice.

1057
01:11:41,048 --> 01:11:42,383
You're going
to be punching guys bigger.

1058
01:11:42,550 --> 01:11:44,510
You're going to have to punch up.

1059
01:11:44,677 --> 01:11:45,761
That's it.

1060
01:11:46,846 --> 01:11:47,847
Nice.

1061
01:11:53,561 --> 01:11:55,855
You, too, old man?

1062
01:11:56,022 --> 01:11:57,899
Come on. Let's get to work.

1063
01:12:00,568 --> 01:12:02,737
Nice! Let's do that again.

1064
01:12:04,530 --> 01:12:06,574
Nice. Three-punch combo.

1065
01:12:07,783 --> 01:12:09,118
Combo.

1066
01:12:10,119 --> 01:12:11,871
Again. Again.

1067
01:12:12,997 --> 01:12:16,417
Faster. Faster. Nice.

1068
01:12:18,085 --> 01:12:20,755
You're not even out of breath.
I like it.

1069
01:12:20,922 --> 01:12:22,256
Let's see how you move.

1070
01:12:28,095 --> 01:12:30,348
[chuckles] That's good.

1071
01:12:34,143 --> 01:12:36,604
[? Bad Meets Evil: "Fast Lane"]

1072
01:12:44,070 --> 01:12:45,821
[crowd cheers]

1073
01:12:57,500 --> 01:12:58,751
[electronic beeping]

1074
01:13:03,089 --> 01:13:05,967
[crowd cheering]

1075
01:13:06,133 --> 01:13:08,719
Step around.
Left hook. Left hook.

1076
01:13:25,319 --> 01:13:26,988
That's it. Every time.

1077
01:13:27,154 --> 01:13:28,864
[mechanical whirring]

1078
01:13:45,047 --> 01:13:46,382
Great fight, fellas.

1079
01:13:54,307 --> 01:13:57,893
<i>[DJ] 105. 5, W-R-U-T,</i>
<i>the satellite home of robot boxing.</i>

1080
01:13:58,060 --> 01:13:59,603
<i>Caller two, what do you got for me?</i>

1081
01:13:59,770 --> 01:14:02,148
<i>[caller] Have you heard about this</i>
<i>little bot out there, his name is Atom?</i>

1082
01:14:02,315 --> 01:14:03,524
<i>[DJ] Oh, yeah. Oh, yeah.</i>

1083
01:14:03,691 --> 01:14:05,901
<i>[caller] My buddies and I saw him</i>
<i>the other night, and he dances.</i>

1084
01:14:06,068 --> 01:14:07,945
<i>- [DJ] Did you say "dances"?</i>
<i>- [caller] You heard me.</i>

1085
01:14:08,112 --> 01:14:09,864
<i>He dances pre-fight</i>
<i>with this little kid,</i>

1086
01:14:10,031 --> 01:14:11,907
<i>and the crowd</i>
<i>went nuts for these two.</i>

1087
01:14:12,074 --> 01:14:13,326
<i>[DJ] I'll tell you what's</i>
<i>really something,</i>

1088
01:14:13,492 --> 01:14:14,744
<i>you put the gimmick</i>
<i>aside for a second</i>

1089
01:14:14,910 --> 01:14:17,455
<i>and I'm holding here</i>
<i>a list of the bots he's beaten.</i>

1090
01:14:17,621 --> 01:14:19,874
<i>Chaos. Wall Street.</i>
<i>One-Eyed Jack.</i>

1091
01:14:20,041 --> 01:14:21,792
<i>No slouches on that list, right?</i>

1092
01:14:21,959 --> 01:14:24,128
<i>But folks,</i>
<i>Atom's fought them all, beat them all.</i>

1093
01:14:24,295 --> 01:14:26,380
<i>[caller] I'm telling you, Tommy,</i>
<i>this bot is fast!</i>

1094
01:14:26,547 --> 01:14:28,716
<i>He escapes shots from</i>
<i>these bigger bots, it's insane!</i>

1095
01:14:28,883 --> 01:14:30,468
<i>[DJ] No doubt, no doubt.</i>
<i>I'm telling you, listeners,</i>

1096
01:14:30,634 --> 01:14:33,888
<i>you remember this name:</i>
<i>Atom. That's right, A-T-O-M.</i>

1097
01:14:34,055 --> 01:14:35,097
[both] Atom!

1098
01:14:35,264 --> 01:14:36,932
<i>[DJ] This bot is one to watch.</i>

1099
01:14:41,854 --> 01:14:44,190
- Awesome fight, sir.
- Thanks, thanks.

1100
01:14:44,357 --> 01:14:46,359
Great fight, guys.

1101
01:14:46,525 --> 01:14:47,860
- Kenton, you guys put on a good show.
- Thanks.

1102
01:14:48,027 --> 01:14:49,904
Good enough, we'd like to invite you
to fight on our card,

1103
01:14:50,071 --> 01:14:51,864
Virgin America Spectrum Detroit,
Friday night.

1104
01:14:52,031 --> 01:14:55,618
Right. Whoa.
That's a WRB... That's a League fight.

1105
01:14:55,785 --> 01:14:58,204
Damn right it is.
What do you say, fellas?

1106
01:14:58,371 --> 01:14:59,830
You ready for the show?

1107
01:15:01,540 --> 01:15:02,708
Heck, yeah.

1108
01:15:02,875 --> 01:15:04,460
[crowd clamoring]

1109
01:15:11,509 --> 01:15:15,304
[Charlie] It's the undercard,
but it's still a League fight.

1110
01:15:15,471 --> 01:15:18,516
I just want you to be relaxed.
I want you to be relaxed, OK, Max.

1111
01:15:18,682 --> 01:15:20,059
No freaking out.

1112
01:15:20,226 --> 01:15:21,602
Don't get all freaky-deaky on me.

1113
01:15:21,769 --> 01:15:24,105
You go freaky-deaky,
this whole thing can go south.

1114
01:15:24,271 --> 01:15:26,273
Whatever you do, have fun, have fun.

1115
01:15:26,440 --> 01:15:27,858
You got to have fun,
you understand me?

1116
01:15:28,025 --> 01:15:30,027
We've come too far to get out there

1117
01:15:30,194 --> 01:15:31,987
and freak out
and blow this whole thing.

1118
01:15:32,154 --> 01:15:35,533
We're going to have fun, and we gonna...
we're gonna not freak out!

1119
01:15:35,699 --> 01:15:39,078
We're going to stay loose,
and we're just going to bam him.

1120
01:15:39,245 --> 01:15:42,790
I tell ya, man, I've spent my whole life
waiting to get here. We're going to...

1121
01:15:43,582 --> 01:15:47,753
Because, I tell ya what... Trust me when
I say no freaking out. You got it?

1122
01:15:47,920 --> 01:15:50,423
- Yeah, I got it.
- Good.

1123
01:15:50,589 --> 01:15:55,761
You have been invited to Lemkova Suite.
Follow me, please.

1124
01:15:55,928 --> 01:15:57,430
What was that? One more time.

1125
01:15:57,596 --> 01:16:00,015
Lemkova Suite. Zeus Suite.

1126
01:16:00,182 --> 01:16:04,395
Sure. Yeah. Let's head
up to the champ's suite. Sure.

1127
01:16:27,293 --> 01:16:30,337
[hip hop music playing]

1128
01:16:33,382 --> 01:16:34,508
[Charlie] Wow.

1129
01:16:34,675 --> 01:16:36,469
Gentlemen, I'm Farra Lemkova.

1130
01:16:36,635 --> 01:16:38,596
Yeah. I'm Charlie Kenton and...

1131
01:16:38,762 --> 01:16:40,723
And this, of course,
is Tak Mashido.

1132
01:16:40,890 --> 01:16:44,059
Holy shit. It's Tak Mashido.

1133
01:16:44,226 --> 01:16:46,353
I know you have
a very important fight tonight,

1134
01:16:46,520 --> 01:16:47,646
so I'll get right to it.

1135
01:16:47,813 --> 01:16:49,565
It's a little far
from the action for my liking.

1136
01:16:49,732 --> 01:16:53,110
It's nice. I like it, though.
Very nicely...

1137
01:16:53,277 --> 01:16:55,196
Wow, that is... That's a great shot.

1138
01:16:55,362 --> 01:16:57,990
Look at that. You want an autograph?
Would you mind...

1139
01:16:58,157 --> 01:16:59,617
I'd like to buy your robot.

1140
01:17:01,827 --> 01:17:03,996
He'd be useful sparring bot for Zeus.

1141
01:17:04,163 --> 01:17:06,165
