1144
01:17:12,671 --> 01:17:15,257
- Of course he is. We can definitely...
- He's not for sale.

1145
01:17:15,424 --> 01:17:17,384
You are 15 minutes away

1146
01:17:17,551 --> 01:17:20,471
from getting in
the ring with Twin Cities,

1147
01:17:20,638 --> 01:17:22,389
a vicious League bot.

1148
01:17:22,556 --> 01:17:26,060
So, to be clear, my offer stands

1149
01:17:26,227 --> 01:17:27,811
until the starting bell.

1150
01:17:27,978 --> 01:17:30,397
OK. And just to be clear,

1151
01:17:30,564 --> 01:17:32,191
he's not for sale!

1152
01:17:32,358 --> 01:17:34,860
Not now, not ever.

1153
01:17:35,027 --> 01:17:37,821
Listen, give me
a minute to clear this up, OK?

1154
01:17:37,988 --> 01:17:40,824
Tak, how are you? Max!

1155
01:17:40,991 --> 01:17:45,579
Max. Max. Be smart.
I know you love him

1156
01:17:45,746 --> 01:17:48,123
but in 20 minutes there
may be nothing left to love.

1157
01:17:48,290 --> 01:17:50,459
Think about it.
Take the offer.

1158
01:17:50,626 --> 01:17:52,920
You think about it.
Why does she want Atom?

1159
01:17:53,087 --> 01:17:55,631
Huh? Because he's
different from other bots!

1160
01:17:55,798 --> 01:17:57,424
Yeah, he's different.
He's smaller and weaker,

1161
01:17:57,591 --> 01:17:58,676
and he's going
to get his ass kicked.

1162
01:17:58,842 --> 01:18:03,264
He's a boxer. We taught him to box.
You taught him to box!

1163
01:18:03,430 --> 01:18:05,391
- That's worth something.
- I think it is, too.

1164
01:18:05,558 --> 01:18:08,811
I think it's worth 200 grand.
Two hundred grand.

1165
01:18:08,978 --> 01:18:11,897
Charlie, we can go round and round
this all night long.

1166
01:18:12,064 --> 01:18:13,524
Look at me, look at me.

1167
01:18:14,817 --> 01:18:16,151
