1180
01:19:46,533 --> 01:19:49,078
[crowd cheers]

1181
01:19:49,244 --> 01:19:51,372
[dance music playing]

1182
01:20:23,987 --> 01:20:26,323
[laughing]

1183
01:20:36,875 --> 01:20:38,585
[whirring]

1184
01:20:38,752 --> 01:20:41,755
[indistinct shouting]

1185
01:20:41,922 --> 01:20:43,215
- Nice work, boss.
- Thanks.

1186
01:20:43,382 --> 01:20:45,634
- Did you switch him to fight mode?
- Of course.

1187
01:20:45,801 --> 01:20:47,469
All right, now this bot
is tough to put down.

1188
01:20:47,636 --> 01:20:48,595
Atom can do it.

1189
01:20:48,762 --> 01:20:53,016
Max, look over there. You see those
geeks with the joysticks and consoles?

