seeing what he sees,

1192
01:20:56,687 --> 01:20:58,105
stadium feeds of the fights, everything.

1193
01:20:58,272 --> 01:21:00,274
This is not like the underground
handheld remote bots

1194
01:21:00,441 --> 01:21:02,651
we've been fighting.
This is the League. Stand on that.

1195
01:21:02,818 --> 01:21:04,361
So what do we do?

1196
01:21:05,112 --> 01:21:08,615
We fight smart,
we be patient. And pray.

1197
01:21:10,117 --> 01:21:11,869
Seriously, pray.

1198
01:21:13,454 --> 01:21:15,164
[referee] Ready!

1199
01:21:16,707 --> 01:21:18,500
- Ready!
- Hands up.

1200
01:21:18,667 --> 01:21:20,919
Fighters ready! Fight!

1201
01:21:21,086 --> 01:21:22,921
[beeping, whirring]

